CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 10, 1970, pg. 15, reads: "Frogs Dinner - Dancing Party Sparks Holiday Season - Among The Guests at the party were this attractive group of ladies. After cicktails [cocktails] and dinner, guests enjoyed dancing to the music of the Bobby Jones Trio. All Courier Photos by 'Teenie' Harris."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of FROGS wives, posed behind long banquet table in Redwood Motor Hotel for FROGS Dinner - Dance party
